sentences: He was also awarded the Asian Film Academy fellowship in 2013 as part of the Busan International Film Festival, Busan, South Korea.
Sanal was awarded the Kerala State Television Award 2016 for the Malayalam short film Chaver.
He started his career as an Assistant Sound Mixer in Shashant Shah's 'Chalo Dilli' in 2010.
Over the years, he has worked in various projects including but not limited to feature films, short films and documentaries as Sound Designer and Production Sound Mixer.
He was the recipient of the 65th National Film Award of India for Best Sound Design for the Ladakhi-language feature film Walking with the Wind, released in the year 2017.
